### Authentication Endpoints

### Register a new user
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@enicarthage.tn",
  "password": "password123",
  "department": "Informatique"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "prof@enicarthage.tn",
  "password": "prof123"
}

###

### Ticket Endpoints (Require Bearer Token)

### Get all tickets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get ticket by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get tickets by status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/status/EN_ATTENTE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get my tickets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/my-tickets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create a ticket (multipart/form-data)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ticket"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cours de Mathématiques",
  "description": "Cours",
  "actProf": "Prof. Dupont",
  "totalNumber": 30
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="cours.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< ./path/to/file.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Create a ticket (JSON only, no file)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tickets
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="ticket"
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "TD Algorithmique",
  "description": "Traveaux Dérigés",
  "actProf": "Prof. Martin",
  "totalNumber": 25
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

###

### Update a ticket
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Cours de Mathématiques - Mis à jour",
  "status": "EN_COURS",
  "totalNumber": 35
}

###

### Delete a ticket (Admin only)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tickets/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

